Package: CEGrplot
Title: Tools for Ocean data Visualization and Auto-save figures-Coastal Ecology Group (CEG) Xiamen University
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("WeinanLi", email = "lwnzjou@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: CEGrplot is an open source package developed by the Coastal Ecology Group (CEG) at Xiamen University.
    It is designed for visualizing oceanographic data and automatically saving the generated figures.
    The Global ETOPO1_15second.nc data included in the package is sourced from NOAA National Centers for Environmental Information. 
    <DOI: 10.25921/fd45-gt74>
    Data interpolation is performed using the mba.surf() function from the "MBA" package.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/WeinanLi/CEGrplot
Encoding: UTF-8
